Type: Package
Package: mixHMMR
Title: Mixture of Hidden Markov Model Regression (mixHMMR) for Simultaneous Curve Clustering and Segmentation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Faicel", "Chamroukhi", role = c("aut"),
    email = "faicel.chamroukhi@unicaen.fr",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5894-3103")),
    person("Marius", "Bartcus", role = c("aut"), 
    email = "marius.bartcus@gmail.com"),
    person("Florian", "Lecocq", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "florian.lecocq@outlook.com"))
Description: Simultaneous model-based clustering and segmentation of heterogeneous and 
    dynamical functional data (curves/times series) with changes in regime by a mixture 
    of gaussian regression models with hidden Markov processes, fitted by the EM/Baum-Welch 
    algorithm. See also the packages 'mixRHLP', 'mixHMM', and 'HMMR'.
License: GPL (>= 3)
